-- Russian state expenditure should decline by at least 5 pct a year - RIA
-- By Polina Devitt
-- Wed Dec 17, 2014 03:24AM EST
-- None



MOSCOW, Dec 17 (Reuters) - Russian state expenditure should fall by at least 5 pct per year over the next three years, RIA news agency quoted Sergei Ivanov, the head of the Kremlin's administration, as saying on Wednesday.

